<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Combat Effects: Normal<BR>Shielding: High<BR>Stun Resist: High<BR>Strikethrough: Low<BR>Spell Shield: Normal<BR>Avoidance: High<BR>Accuracy: High<BR>DOT Shielding: Normal</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Skill Mods: Dodge and Parry would be nice, but there isn't too many items with those for a long time<BR>Click Effects: This is the single most important thing.&nbsp; This alone can determine if I want an item or not.&nbsp; For example, the following items may not have good stats (compare to other items that I can have), but they are very much wanted on my list</DIV>
<DIV>Prismatic Ring of Resistance - AC + Resist clickie</DIV>
<DIV>Stormeye Band&nbsp; - The clickie is not important, but this is an inventory instant clickie</DIV>
<DIV>Pendant of Discord - FT clickie, which imho is a must have for Knights (Rangers and BST would be better served using the overhaste clickie)<BR>Proc Effects: Not important<BR>Worn Effects: Haste, Improved Dodge, Improved Parry, Ferocity, Cleave are pretty much all the tank worn effects that I consider must have<BR>Focus Effects: Healing Mod, Beneficial Spell Haste, and Mana Conservation, Extend Beneficial Duration&nbsp;are what I consider must have for Paladins.&nbsp; Distance Mod would be nice also.</DIV>
				
